Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.37,0:07:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}當初我和紗夜經常為了願望券對決呢
