Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}然後我們倆一起挑戰了遙姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.65,0:07:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我當然記得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你的刀法比以前大有長進啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這都要歸功於基礎訓練呢
