Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}爸爸只讓我 進行基礎訓練 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:07:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}紗夜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.13,0:08:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}配合得還真不錯...
