Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}哎呀 剛才那招確實讓我慌了一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這樣的話如果我不拿出真本事反倒是失禮了呢
