Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}夭霧辰明流奧傳之- 「逆羅剎」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.85,0:09:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}「逆羅剎」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}結果在那之後也一次都沒贏過遙姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}因為姐姐真的非常強啊
