Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這一點嘛 綾斗也一樣
