Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.90,0:10:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}所以綾斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}艱難的時候去求助他人就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}除了我之外肯定還有其他人願意助你一臂之力的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}雖然有些不甘心就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}根據以往的比賽來看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這對雙胞胎自始至終都會針對對手的弱點來攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}他們只在創造出對自己絕對有利的局面之後才會發動攻勢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}非常難對付的類型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.57,0:10:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過唯獨這次我們也具備一個優勢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.10,0:10:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}優勢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.57,0:10:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}既然那對雙胞胎會針對對手的弱點來攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.69,0:11:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那我們這組應該是弱點最顯而易見的對手了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.49,0:11:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我的封印嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.13,0:11:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這麼一來他們會採取的戰術自然也就非常清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.93,0:11:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}拖延時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我們要在這個基礎上考慮用什麼對策
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我現在只能想到這麼一個辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.13,0:11:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好了終於迎來四分之一決賽的最後一場比賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.69,0:11:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}而且其它擂台上的比賽已經全部結束
