Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}首先進場的是星導館學園
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.29,0:11:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}夭霧綾斗&尤莉絲...愛雷克西亞· 馮· 裏斯妃特組合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.90,0:11:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}另一邊則是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.65,0:11:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}界龍第七學園的黎沈雲...黎沈華組合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}備受矚目的一戰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}雙方都已經進入擂台
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.47,0:12:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}都暴露出那麼大的弱點了竟然沒有臨陣脫逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.00,0:12:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}究竟是膽量夠大還是單純人蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.63,0:12:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}又或者是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}有什麼對策呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}只是我們沒有服輸的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.99,0:12:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}雖然不知道你們有什麼策略不過我非常期待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.76,0:12:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}反正最後贏的人是我們
