Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}以內藏秘劍破星牢之獄解放吾之虎威
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.63,0:12:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}出現了出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.31,0:12:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}夭霧選手的華麗表演
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}啊不對那個貌似不是表演來著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.59,0:12:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好像有很多人認為那是解放原本受限的力量所必需的形式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:12:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}原來如此原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.51,0:12:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}就在我們解說的時候
