Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}鳳凰星武祭四分之一決賽第四回合比賽開始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}真快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過事先已經料到的話也並非躲不過去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}華麗綻放吧九輪舞焰花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}急急如律令敕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.63,0:13:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.19,0:13:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}比賽剛一開始就出現了煙幕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這是打算躲在煙霧中戰鬥的戰術嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.19,0:13:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}沒想到會來這一手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}尤莉絲這些煙霧估計是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}原來如此幻影嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.95,0:14:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}受不了呀最近的觀眾太沒耐心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過對我們來說已經足夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好了比賽已經開始一分鐘了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}對於據稱力量只能發揮 5 分鐘的天霧選手而言
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}接下來的 1 分鐘非常關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.47,0:14:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這兩個傢伙性格確實惡劣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.39,0:14:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}哦呀這邊的也心急得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.71,0:14:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那麼我也...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好了這麼一來我們這邊就準備完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}要是等你們主動攻擊也有點太無趣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.08,0:14:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}而且觀眾們也肯定會覺得很無聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}要是不勁爆一點說不定又會遭噓的
